    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Sever the Soul (Rank 5, Legendary)</p><p>Cost: 5 Gnosis  </p><p>Activation: Action  </p><p>You reach beyond flesh and bone, striking directly at a creature’s animating essence and severing its connection to the material world.</p><p>As an action, choose one creature at or below half of its hit point maximum. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw against your Gift save DC or be reduced to 0 hit points.</p><p>Creatures that possess Legendary Resistance are immune to this effect unless the DM rules otherwise.</p><p>Aftereffects:</p><p>• You gain 3 levels of exhaustion.</p><p></p>",
